==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cash register
<hw>Cash register</hw>. <def>A device for recording the amount of cash
received, usually having an automatic adding machine and a money drawer
and exhibiting the amount of the sale.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

